description: Today I met a cute guy, who was sent to Prague by his employer. He worked as a salesman at a phone company and was supposed to get extra training. He was from a small town, so he decided to turn the whole trip into a regular vacation in the capital. The dude didn't want to be bothered by his co-workers, so he rented a small flat just for himself. He wanted privacy in case he got lucky. And he got incredibly lucky when he met me. The 12 000 Crowns he made was a nice boost to his party budget. I was probably not the type of person he expected to bring to his love place. Still, the dude did his part and earned the money. I'm sure he brought a cute girl next time. I wonder if he told her how he had to bend over like a bitch and take my horny cock up the ass. Or how he cummed for my pleasure...
title: Czech Hunter 490
